 about inefficiency and measurement uncertainty lack quantitative support. Include specific error margins or literature sources to substantiate these TOK considerations.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "a58a4032-eaf6-4943-a215-e626f027220a", "versionId": "218c86ff-7f17-4d42-a587-556ad8818f01", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "suggestion", "pageNumber": 2, "bbox": {"x": 198.33, "y": 72.73, "width": 195.99999999999997, "height": 11.86}, "polygon": [{"x": 198.33, "y": 72.73}, {"x": 394.33, "y": 72.73}, {"x": 394.33, "y": 84.59}, {"x": 198.33, "y": 84.59}], "comment": "The header clearly labels the Wi-Fi router as Object 2, but naming the specific model or brand would enhance authenticity and precision.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "49621c99-3b4a-4438-9691-951e442ac687", "versionId": "218c86ff-7f17-4d42-a587-556ad8818f01", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "suggestion", "pageNumber": 1, "bbox": {"x": 106.08, "y": 85.93, "width": 407.45, "height": 12.539999999999992}, "polygon": [{"x": 106.08, "y": 85.93}, {"x": 513.53, "y": 85.93}, {"x": 513.53, "y": 98.47}, {"x": 106.08, "y": 98.47}], "comment": "The student correctly states the IA prompt but does not reframe it in their own words to establish a clear focus for the exhibition\u00e2\u0080\u0099s analysis.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "965c6eb4-7f7c-494a-bf40-9dba915f38dc", "versionId": "218c86ff-7f17-4d42-a587-556ad8818f01", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "suggestion", "pageNumber": 1, "bbox": {"x": 209.91, "y": 145.34, "width": 175.98, "height": 12.329999999999984}, "polygon": [{"x": 209.91, "y": 145.34}, {"x": 385.89, "y": 145.34}, {"x": 385.89, "y": 157.67}, {"x": 209.91, "y": 157.67}], "comment": "The image caption identifies the pantometer but would be strengthened by specifying when and where the photograph was taken to ground its real-world context.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "2a58a8f3-1b90-4416-b6aa-8fccd6b88913", "versionId": "218c86ff-7f17-4d42-a587-556ad8818f01", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "strength", "pageNumber": 1, "bbox": {"x": 70.47, "y": 384.64, "width": 455.05999999999995, "height": 302.77}, "polygon": [{"x": 70.47, "y": 384.64}, {"x": 525.53, "y": 384.64}, {"x": 525.53, "y": 687.41}, {"x": 70.47, "y": 687.41}], "comment": "The student situates the pantometer in authentic fieldwork, clearly defining its real-world context and linking it to geographic knowledge acquisition.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "124a0007-2bcc-4176-8c9d-36c2d9656721", "versionId": "218c86ff-7f17-4d42-a587-556ad8818f01", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "strength", "pageNumber": 2, "bbox": {"x": 70.47, "y": 330.65, "width": 454.30999999999995, "height": 362.52}, "polygon": [{"x": 70.47, "y": 330.65}, {"x": 524.78, "y": 330.65}, {"x": 524.78, "y": 693.17}, {"x": 70.47, "y": 693.17}], "comment": "The student effectively discusses how the router democratizes knowledge access, demonstrating insight into material tools\u00e2\u0080\u0099 roles in distributing information globally.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "7187631b-9a5b-4fce-9ca0-43048e3989cf", "versionId": "218c86ff-7f17-4d42-a587-556ad8818f01", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 2, "bbox": {"x": 70.47, "y": 330.65, "width": 454.30999999999995, "height": 362.52}, "polygon": [{"x": 70.47, "y": 330.65}, {"x": 524.78, "y": 330.65}, {"x": 524.78, "y": 693.17}, {"x": 70.47, "y": 693.17}], "comment": "Discussion of misinformation is valuable but would be more convincing with concrete examples or studies illustrating how online errors propagate.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "61f7fb7b-7044-4229-9b29-4a1040055122", "versionId": "218c86ff-7f17-4d42-a587-556ad8818f01", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "suggestion", "pageNumber": 3, "bbox": {"x": 143.94, "y": 72.73, "width": 308.87, "height": 12.429999999999993}, "polygon": [{"x": 143.94, "y": 72.73}, {"x": 452.81, "y": 72.73}, {"x": 452.81, "y": 85.16}, {"x": 143.94, "y": 85.16}], "comment": "Consider specifying the exact model of the graphical display calculator to provide greater context and credibility to your analysis.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "8140b2b0-5a61-4119-89c5-564d5e6bcb85", "versionId": "218c86ff-7f17-4d42-a587-556ad8818f01", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "strength", "pageNumber": 3, "bbox": {"x": 70.47, "y": 425.12, "width": 454.30999999999995, "height": 273.80999999999995}, "polygon": [{"x": 70.47, "y": 425.12}, {"x": 524.78, "y": 425.12}, {"x": 524.78, "y": 698.93}, {"x": 70.47, "y": 698.93}], "comment": "The student correctly links human error in data entry to tool reliability, showing a solid TOK understanding of how material tools can both enable and constrain knowledge.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "b988ac79-0208-4494-b725-702000cc79a7", "versionId": "218c86ff-7f17-4d42-a587-556ad8818f01", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 3, "bbox": {"x": 70.47, "y": 425.12, "width": 454.30999999999995, "height": 273.80999999999995}, "polygon": [{"x": 70.47, "y": 425.12}, {"x": 524.78, "y": 425.12}, {"x": 524.78, "y": 698.93}, {"x": 70.47, "y": 698.93}], "comment": "Analysis remains largely anecdotal; incorporating TOK literature or empirical studies on calculator limitations would deepen the critical evaluation.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}]}]}}, "rubricData": {"id": 57, "rubricId": "15a001d0-4b6b-41b6-abae-4e9498385eaf", "version": 1, "status": "published", "createdAt": "2025-02-20T06:03:43.512Z", "name": "TOK Exhibition", "totalMarks": 10, "description": null, "type": "TOK", "rubricSpecificInfo": null, "slug": "tok-exhibition", "tags": [""], "isArchived": false, "currentRevisionId": 57, "gradeBoundaryId": "52ad2701-27bc-42f3-be3f-d63b98d98139", "criteria": [{"id": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "groupName": "TOK Exhibition", "orderIndex": 0, "isGradable": true, "showGradedScore": true, "description": null, "bands": [{"id": "9ff6a42c-458d-4ba2-aed7-d0ce052fc68b", "marksFrom": 0, "marksTo": 0, "orderIndex": 0, "strands": [{"id": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "name": "Does the exhibition successfully show how TOK manifests in the world around us?", "orderIndex": 0, "content": "The exhibition does not reach the standard described by the other levels or does not use one of the IA prompts provided."}]}, {"id": "a1ba39dd-f4e1-46d0-92fb-f804616659df", "marksFrom": 1, "marksTo": 2, "orderIndex": 1, "strands": [{"id": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "name": "Does the exhibition successfully show how TOK manifests in the world around us?", "orderIndex": 0, "content": "The exhibition presents\nthree objects, but the\nreal-world contexts of\nthese objects are not\nstated, or the images\npresented may be\nhighly generic images of\ntypes of object rather\nthan of specific\nreal-world objects. Links\nbetween the objects\nand the selected IA\nprompt are made, but\nthese are minimal,\ntenuous, or it is not\nclear what the student is\ntrying to convey.\nThere is very little\njustification offered for\nthe inclusion of each\nobject in the exhibition.\nThe commentary on the\nobjects is highly\ndescriptive or consists\nonly of unsupported\nassertions."}]}, {"id": "d33f3613-07e3-4130-984c-f84b6431e3e4", "marksFrom": 3, "marksTo": 4, "orderIndex": 2, "strands": [{"id": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "name": "Does the exhibition successfully show how TOK manifests in the world around us?", "orderIndex": 0, "content": "The exhibition identifies three objects, although the real-world contexts of the objects may be implied rather than explicitly stated. Basic links between the objects and the selected IA prompt are made, but the explanation of these links is unconvincing and/or unfocused. There is a superficial justification for the inclusion of each object in the exhibition. Reasons for the inclusion of the objects are offered, but these are not supported by appropriate evidence and/or lack relevance to the selected IA prompt. There may be significant repetition across the justifications of the different objects"}]}, {"id": "bd39c308-b52c-4662-b0f5-64d285be9e95", "marksFrom": 5, "marksTo": 6, "orderIndex": 3, "strands": [{"id": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "name": "Does the exhibition successfully show how TOK manifests in the world around us?", "orderIndex": 0, "content": "The exhibition identifies three objects, although the real-world contexts of these objects may be vaguely or imprecisely stated. There is some explanation of the links between the three objects and the selected IA prompt. There is some justification for the inclusion of each object in the exhibition. Some of the points are supported by evidence and references to the selected IA prompt."}]}, {"id": "48708361-8824-4c01-bcbd-39c3e493de8e", "marksFrom": 7, "marksTo": 8, "orderIndex": 4, "strands": [{"id": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "name": "Does the exhibition successfully show how TOK manifests in the world around us?", "orderIndex": 0, "content": "The exhibition identifies three objects and their real-world contexts. Links between each of the three objects and the selected IA prompt are explained, although this explanation may lack precision and clarity in parts. There is a justification of the contribution that each individual object makes to the exhibition. Many of the points are supported by appropriate evidence and references to the selected IA prompt."}]}, {"id": "5552e9fd-0d0a-4bb2-9ece-5e7a3c438771", "marksFrom": 9, "marksTo": 10, "orderIndex": 5, "strands": [{"id": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "name": "Does the exhibition successfully show how TOK manifests in the world around us?", "orderIndex": 0, "content": "The exhibition clearly identifies three objects and their specific real-world contexts. Links between each of the three objects and the selected IA prompt are clearly made and well-explained. There is a strong justification of the particular contribution that each individual object makes to the exhibition. All, or nearly all, of the points are well-supported by appropriate evidence and explicit references to the selected IA prompt."}]}]}], "rubricCriteria": [{"id": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "rubricId": "15a001d0-4b6b-41b6-abae-4e9498385eaf", "revisionId": 57, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition", "label": null, "orderIndex": 0, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:03:55.358727+00", "updatedAt": "2025-07-16 11:21:18.828885+00", "isGradable": true, "showGradedScore": true, "isChecklistCriterion": false, "description": null, "rubricCriterionBands": [{"id": "9ff6a42c-458d-4ba2-aed7-d0ce052fc68b", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "marksFrom": 0, "marksTo": 0, "orde